title: 09/08/21 DPS Hour 2 Chip Kelly
itunes:title: 09/08/21 DPS Hour 2 Chip Kelly
description:
In this hour of The Dan Patrick Show, former UCF quarterback and current Florida State Seminole McKenzie Milton discusses his incredible return from a gruesome knee injury to playing this past Saturday against Notre Dame. Plus, UCLA head football coach Chip Kelly joins the program to talk about the strengths of his now-ranked Bruins, being mistaken for a certain celebrity in Los Angeles, and the underrated sense of humor of New England head coach Bill Belichick.
